{"word":"ἀμφικύπελλος","slug":"ἀμφικύπελλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n5911\" key=\"a)mfiku/pellos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀμφικύπελλος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">δέπας ἀ.</orth> <sense id=\"n5911.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">double cup,</tr_> such as forms a <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κύπελλον</foreign> both at top and bottom, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:584\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.584</biblScope></bibl>,al.: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφικύπελλα</foreign> are compared with the cell of a honeycomb, as possessing <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφίστομοι θυρίδες,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:624a:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">624a9</biblScope> </bibl>; but acc. to <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author></bibl>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">two-handled,</tr_> cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:783b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.783b</biblScope> </bibl> (post <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:466c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.466c</biblScope> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}